{"id":8902,"date":"2025-09-02T12:24:25","date_gmt":"2025-09-02T12:24:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/oorwin.ai\/?post_type=knowledge_base&#038;p=8902"},"modified":"2025-09-05T10:49:34","modified_gmt":"2025-09-05T10:49:34","slug":"share-a-job-with-an-account-contact","status":"publish","type":"knowledge_base","link":"https:\/\/oorwin.ai\/knowledge-base\/share-a-job-with-an-account-contact\/","title":{"rendered":"Share a Job with an Account Contact"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"8902\" class=\"elementor elementor-8902\" data-elementor-settings=\"{&quot;ha_cmc_init_switcher&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-elementor-post-type=\"knowledge_base\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c2ee936 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7c2ee936\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f9a568f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f9a568f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-9cb2dfefdd07ca874f73b77708167a7b\">Users can share a job with an account contact directly from the <strong>Account View Page<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\">Steps to Share a Job with an Account Contact :<\/h2>\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-4f6c9eefe4049e593ced42a64a2a4d7a\">Log in to your Oorwin account and navigate to the <strong>Accounts<\/strong> module from the left menu under the <strong>General<\/strong> section.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-4ef68207aee8e00c8dc0ec00b79626b0\">Select the account whose contact you want to share a job with.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-7f677bdf02d3ec2b8e0fe427caf47e1f\">Click on the <strong>Contacts<\/strong> tab in the top header.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-8d58076972e00774a434130a06f3a177\">Choose the desired contact and click the <strong>More (three dots)<\/strong> icon next to their name.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-06364e0be57357ff396452f87300dbc1\">From the actions list, select <strong>Share Job<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-ae8a28778f28a0b3c86f453e573ee792\">A popup will appear displaying the list of jobs you have access to.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-98c8e5f4b52961476c2fb48130ad91d8\">Select the job you want to share with this contact.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-b2cb9c0af34ec7a9dccc8813763a4f5e\">A <strong>Share Job compose mail<\/strong> popup will open with pre-filled content.<\/li>\n\n<li class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-ad09621e2a8d1d31e4b7c19cde0fddf4\">Add additional recipients or details if needed, and then click <strong>Send<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p class=\"has-ast-global-color-7-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-401ea2f3155a310ec0bf241280152b3b\">\u2705 The job has now been successfully shared with the selected contact.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Users can share a job with an account contact directly from the Account View Page. Steps to Share a Job [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","a